name: Entrainment
summary: Changes the target's ability to the user's. Fails if the target has the ability Trace, Truant, Multitype, Flower Gift, Illusion, Imposter, Zen Mode, or Stance Change.
viability: Entrainment is good in Doubles if you want to mess with your opponent. A good troll strategy is to use Entrainment with Truant Durant. While it's not the best strategy out there, it is pretty fun to set up.
